  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[On Play] Reveal the top 3 cards of your deck. Add 1 [Tapirmon]
    and 1 2-color black card among them to your hand. Place the rest at the bottom
    of your deck in any order. [Your Turn] When one of your Digimon would digivolve
    into a 2-color black Digimon card, you may suspend this Tamer to reduce the digivolution
    cost by 1.'
